text: Jaffa can stand for different concepts: *It is the name of a city in Israel, which is part of Tel Aviv today (the full name of that city is Tel-Aviv-Jaffa) *It is the name of a cultivar of oranges, called Jaffa orange. The orange was first grown near the city. *Jaffa Cakes a kind of pastry named after the orange.
title: Jaffa (disambigation)
